OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 22 May to Sun 31 May
OL,6,FHigh pressure is expected to bring a
OL,7,Fgood deal of fair, warm weather to the
OL,8,FUK during the Bank Holiday weekend. It
OL,9,Fmay be cloudier with a chance of some
OL,10,Fshowers across Northern Ireland and
OL,11,FScotland, but even here it will be
OL,12,Fmuch warmer than the previous week and
OL,13,Fthere will be plenty of dry weather
OL,14,Faround too. Through the following
OL,15,Fweek, high pressure is expected to
OL,16,Fbroadly remain in place for much of
OL,17,Fthe UK, and fine weather is likely to
OL,18,Fcontinue for most of the country.
OL,19,FThere may be occasions where low
OL,20,Fpressure to the north may bring some
OL,21,Fbrief spells of rain across northern
OL,22,Fparts, but in general fair weather
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,23,Fwill dominate. Temperatures are
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
OL,24,Fexpected to be above normal, feeling
OL,25,Fvery warm at times with light winds.
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
PN,16303
SC,0003
CT,20,T
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1779030723
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 1 Jun to Mon 15 Jun
OL,6,FFair weather is more likely to
OL,7,Fdominate, at least at first. Rain and
OL,8,Fshowers are possible at times, mainly
OL,9,Facross Northern Ireland and Scotland,
OL,10,Fbut the main emphasis remains for fine
OL,11,Fand dry weather for most places. As we
OL,12,Fhead towards mid-June, more mixed
OL,13,Fconditions are likely with spells of
OL,14,Frain and showers. Drier weather is
OL,15,Fexpected between any bouts of wetter
OL,16,Fweather, these drier interludes will
OL,17,Ftend to last longer across the south
OL,18,Fand east of England. Temperatures are
OL,19,Fmost likely to be near or slightly
OL,20,Fabove average overall, with some warm
OL,21,For very warm weather possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,164,160,301,260,100,100
